subject: Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Jelena Jankovic, ranked No. 3 in the world, nearly saw her ambitions unravel at Wimbledon, before she rallied to beat Lucie Safarova 5-7, 7-6 (4), 6-2.
